snippet.title: White Room: Mind’s Prison | Southeast Asia Games Onward 2024 Trailer
snippet.description:
White Room: Mind's Prison is a psychological horror game. You're not allowed to make any sound. Entities will make you scream. Stay quiet! The day counter will increase as you survive! Survive as long as possible. MICROPHONE REQUIRED!
